Kilombero Sugar of Tanzania Fires Can Harvesters, Guardian Says

-- B y   D a v i d   M a l i n g h a   D o y a
-- 
2011-08-22T08:16:29Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-22/kilombero-sugar-of-tanzania-fires-can-harvesters-guardian-says.html
Kilombero Sugar Co. fired all of its
1,400 sugar harvesters after they continued a so-called go-slow
even after being granted a wage increase, the Dar es Salaam-
based  Guardian  newspaper reported, without citing anyone.  Kilombero, owned by  South Africa ’s  Illovo Sugar Ltd. (ILV) , is
Tanzania’s biggest producer of the sweetener.  To contact the reporter on this story:
David Malingha Doya in  Dar es Salaam  via Nairobi at
   pmrichardson@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
 Paul Richardson  at 
 pmrichardson@bloomberg.net . 